{"id": "1215665479360970782", "channel_id": "1215665479360970782", "type": 0, "author_id": "1151924228417921134", "author_name": "kei_0625", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T14:20:36.252000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1215665480065486889", "filename": "Image_1709907577583.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1332069, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215665479360970782/1215665480065486889/Image_1709907577583.png?ex=6a009434&is=69ff42b4&hm=423adcf301bad0ae70959e21d0fdf9dcc613f2abffe4313da4b36454ae6cba40&"}, {"id": "1215665480631582720", "filename": "Image_1709907582199.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1090153, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215665479360970782/1215665480631582720/Image_1709907582199.png?ex=6a009434&is=69ff42b4&hm=c372ad3e5ba9c326d2affa4aefac6fee2ad8dc04b7ca8a56eff5b163b56d3087&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215665479360970782", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」H 6-6成就bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1215698301261844480", "channel_id": "1215698301261844480", "type": 0, "author_id": "1195028389589958687", "author_name": "busy_chipmunk_73748_41947", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻梦深潜是日常玩法的重要组成，在无活动时是玩家近乎唯一的玩法（除pvp）\n所以深潜的游戏性极为重要。\n这次改版呢对我个人看来是比之前要好。因为我讨厌一些要抠的细节分与对慢速阵容不友好的回合限制，以及会影响打法与阵容的任务。（任务和细节这俩点看法比较个人，比如有要过牌什么的任务就要在阵容选择上做出改变，不然做起来很麻烦，讨厌这种强制改变打法的东西）\n改版后，强制600死抗非常糟糕，逼迫让玩家带一些死扛命轮。还有融灾机制对混沌界域与盾击及需要狂气回转的阵容很不友好\n我建议是提供一些debuff与给敌方增强的buff让玩家自行根据自己的阵容选择（如己方战斗开始时获得虚弱，敌方生命之上升等）然后每周和每天进行词条的轮换。结算分数为(基础分数+词条分数)×关卡等级倍率", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T16:31:01.603000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1215698301580746772", "filename": "Screenshot_20240308_223829.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 114721, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215698301261844480/1215698301580746772/Screenshot_20240308_223829.jpg?ex=6a00b2c5&is=69ff6145&hm=bad7880df76b04fc6649dbc5fd2eae59cb58dc49625e95f6b5a4996e07f2c419&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215698301261844480", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "浅谈一下幻梦深潜与一些建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
