{"id": "1215504410243768352", "channel_id": "1215504410243768352", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛點進物資介面時，命輪排序是根據稀有度「從高至低」，\n切換到其他物資例如密契後，如果再切回命輪頁面，\n命輪排序就自動變成稀有度「從低至高」排序，\n不確定是不是只有我的帳號遇上這個問題。\nUID: 100253707", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T03:40:34.382000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-08T03:41:28.606000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215504410243768352", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」物資命輪排序問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
